== Methods to Fight Lavos ==

=== Standard Method ===

Enter the Black Omen and fight through to Lavos, or use the bucket at End of Time.

=== Epoch Method ===

Ram the Epoch into Lavos (destroys the Epoch). Skips outer shell battle.

=== Ocean Palace ===

Fight Lavos during the Ocean Palace sequence (scripted loss normally).

=== Telepod Method ===

New Game+ only: Use right telepod at beginning to fight Lavos immediately.

