== Tips for Ending Hunters ==

=== Save Points ===

Create saves at these points:
* Before telepod (NG+) - Ending 3
* After Leene rescue - Ending 4
* After trial - Ending 5
* 600 A.D. arrival - Ending 6
* Before Masamune quest - Ending 7
* After Masamune - Ending 8
* After Magus fight - Ending 9
* After Azala - Ending 10
* Dark Ages arrival - Ending 11
* After Ocean Palace - Ending 12, 1, 2

=== Quick Lavos Strategies ===

For NG+ ending runs:
* Level 40+ characters trivialize Lavos
* Luminaire + Flare combo
* Triple Techs for quick damage
* Epoch ram skips outer shell

